When add dependency `spring-cloud-services-starter-config-client`, threre's `RetryTemplate` in your project. So `SpringAiRetryAutoConfiguration ` start run.
```
@AutoConfiguration
@ConditionalOnClass(RetryTemplate.class)
@EnableConfigurationProperties({ SpringAiRetryProperties.class })
public class SpringAiRetryAutoConfiguration {}
```
For the time being, I think you can make the project keep running normally by add `spring-ai-retry` dependency.
To fix it, the `@ConditionalOnClass(RetryTemplate.class)` might need to be replaced with another class relevant to `spring-ai-retry`.
